00:19:51,320 --> 00:19:51,960
That's so funny.

218
00:19:51,960 --> 00:19:58,880
So, I ended up deciding that actually, I'm just 
ready. I'm ready to move on. I spent enough  

219
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:04,360
time at this company, at this product 
trying to shape it into something  

