232
00:21:07,840 --> 00:21:13,360
Yeah. You've touched on this. You're 
known for at Twitter someone that  

233
00:21:13,360 --> 00:21:18,560
turned the culture of the product team and 
Twitter in general from a very stagnant,  

234
00:21:18,560 --> 00:21:22,200
nothing-is-changing product to shipping 
