280
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:47,480
And listen, as much as I was kind of throwing 
stones from the sidelines through that period  

281
00:25:47,480 --> 00:25:51,840
when I was in Periscope land in our separate 
office a few blocks away from the mothership,  

282
00:25:51,840 --> 00:25:57,320
that focus actually did help the company for 
some period. The reason why Twitter went from  

283
00:25:57,320 --> 00:26:04,120
