feeling that the product was changed at all. 

294
00:26:58,240 --> 00:27:01,880
Because you would hear people, I mean, one of 
the beautiful things about working on Twitter  

295
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:08,160
as a product is that you have literally customers 
being injected into your veins. Every single day,  

296
00:27:08,160 --> 00:27:11,480
whatever you change about a product or whatever 
you don't change, they're telling you what  

297
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:17,440
