551
00:50:03,040 --> 00:50:10,640
the examples I think was the Amazon. When you get 
order confirmation from Amazon, they intentionally  

552
00:50:10,640 --> 00:50:15,440
bury the order details. You have to click the link 
and authenticate to go see what you ordered. I  

