594
00:53:33,400 --> 00:53:37,360
when you've gone too far with a framework 
like signs like you have implemented this  

595
00:53:37,360 --> 00:53:41,720
to religiously and maybe you should 
be thinking a little more broadly.

596
00:53:41,720 --> 00:53:47,280
There's two, I think, simple and obvious ones. 
One is if the result of your framework is that  

597
00:53:47,280 --> 00:53:52,440
