610
00:55:02,560 --> 00:55:08,200
over time would improve some metric DAU or 
otherwise, like a product like Spaces. In  

611
00:55:08,200 --> 00:55:13,960
order for Spaces to be actually used, you needed 
to make sure that when Lenny starts a Space that  

612
00:55:13,960 --> 00:55:18,840
people would join. And how do you get people to 
