623
00:56:09,280 --> 00:56:16,200
a bunch of bets that the organization then 
sees is disincentivized to make successful,  

624
00:56:16,200 --> 00:56:18,480
then something's got to change.
Either your strategy is just not  

625
00:56:18,480 --> 00:56:24,320
the right strategy because it doesn't abide by the 
