627
00:56:28,800 --> 00:56:34,640
show up as blips on our DAU radar or are going 
to help some other metric that's important. And  

628
00:56:34,640 --> 00:56:40,760
so that took us some time to get, and we tried a 
variety of schemes to make that work. Community  

629
00:56:40,760 --> 00:56:46,280
Notes, the project that I was mentioning Keith 
started, we intentionally structured that like a  

