Mark says, "Hey, you 300 people, stop what you're  

718
01:04:51,600 --> 01:04:55,120
doing. Go basically make live exist in our product 
as a first [inaudible 01:04:56] experience."

719
01:04:55,120 --> 01:04:56,720
Oh, wow. I didn't know that.

